#. <section class="sutta" id="sn15.11"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn15.11:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 15"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 15"

#. </p><p>
#. VAR: 2. Dutiyavagga → duggatavaggo (bj)
msgctxt "sn15.11:0.2"
msgid "2. Dutiyavagga"
msgstr "2. The Second Chapter"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn15.11:0.3"
msgid "11. Duggatasutta"
msgstr "11. In a Bad Way"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn15.11:1.1"
msgid "Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati."
msgstr "At one time the Buddha was staying near Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn15.11:1.2"
msgid "Tatra kho … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn15.11:1.3"
msgid "“Anamataggoyaṃ, bhikkhave, saṃsāro."
msgstr "“Mendicants, transmigration has no known beginning."

msgctxt "sn15.11:1.4"
msgid ""
"Pubbā koṭi na paññāyati avijjānīvaraṇānaṃ sattānaṃ taṇhāsaṃyojanānaṃ "
"sandhāvataṃ saṃsarataṃ."
msgstr ""
"No first point is found of sentient beings roaming and transmigrating, "
"hindered by ignorance and fettered by craving."

msgctxt "sn15.11:1.5"
msgid "Yaṃ, bhikkhave, passeyyātha duggataṃ durūpetaṃ niṭṭhamettha gantabbaṃ:"
msgstr "When you see someone in a bad way, in distress, you should conclude:"

msgctxt "sn15.11:1.6"
msgid "‘amhehipi evarūpaṃ paccanubhūtaṃ iminā dīghena addhunā’ti."
msgstr "‘In all this long time, we too have undergone the same thing.’"

msgctxt "sn15.11:1.7"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu … pe …"
msgstr "Why is that? Transmigration has no known beginning. …"

msgctxt "sn15.11:1.8"
msgid ""
"yāvañcidaṃ, bhikkhave, alameva sabbasaṅkhāresu nibbindituṃ alaṃ virajjituṃ "
"alaṃ vimuccitun”ti."
msgstr ""
"This is quite enough for you to become disillusioned, dispassionate, and "
"freed regarding all conditions.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn15.11:1.9"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
